{"tid":406751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今時今日既小朋友真係慘","createTime":"2017-09-20T02:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T03:26:34.000Z","uid":17313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd054a5a6c39ff2fc0ad7eea89fff9b4386bd96","tid":406751,"uid":17313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:12:59.000Z","msg":"是咁的 今日出旺角睇醫生<br />\n搭巴士個陣就聽到有個女人係咁鬧自己個女<br />\n望一望個小朋友大約一/二年班左右<br />\n個呀媽係咁鬧佢 問佢個死人腦係咪無帶番學校<br />\n不斷係到鬧佢死蠢 無撚用之類既說話<br />\n最令我無奈既係點解個呀媽可以係個女面前講粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬧佢個原因只不過係個小朋友唔識寫牙齒呢兩個字<br />\n之後問佢書 個小朋友又唔係好識某d字<br />\n呢個時候個呀媽又鬧佢：呢d咁簡單既字你都唔識 你個死人腦係咪唔見左 老師最憎就係你呢d人<br />\n個小朋友就勁唔開心咁抱住個頭<br />\n個樣就好似呢個咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65dc8d1913c2ce4d62a4a815781667daa23929b7","tid":406751,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:21:23.000Z","msg":"冇來過世上最好"},{"pid":"d6433ae850a0da776ecce0f5a08ffaff1bd88632","tid":406751,"uid":105654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:14:53.000Z","msg":"好慘......"},{"pid":"de1a82ba8f23b9413c233d8c1bf08464036e6b35","tid":406751,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:26:34.000Z","msg":"香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}